    "description": "ACTUS DeFi ETH 1-minute loan with per-second rate resets and per-second ETH price index.\nMarket factor indexes modeled per-second for one minute (61 data points each, Mar 03 2026 T09:00:00-T09:01:00).\nDeFi Rate: ~7.1590% rising to ~7.1594% over the minute (interpolated from minutely anchors).\nETH price: ~$2371.34 rising to ~$2371.37 with realistic second-level micro-movement.\nPrepayment checks at 15-second intervals: T09:00:15, T09:00:30, T09:00:45, T09:01:00.\nRate resets per-second via cycleOfRateReset=PT1SL1 starting T09:00:01.\nSingle interest payment bullet at maturity T09:01:00. Notional $5000, contract rate 5%.\ndayCountConvention AA365S (second-precision A/365) used for sub-day accrual.\nRun with Collection Runner. No data file needed.\nOpen Postman Console (View > Show Postman Console) to see detailed output.",
